:"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"午高峰的电梯队伍，我正常的排着队伍<br /><br />电梯门开了，我迈了一步要往电梯里进，但就在这个时候一个穿着黄色衣服的送外卖的一边嘟囔着什么，一边非常用力的往里面挤，挤到了我的前面，我一只脚还在空中，被挤了一个大趔趄。<br /><br />电梯里满满当当，黄衣服却当作什么事都没发生，占着本来该属于我的空间。<br /><br />如果说插队还能忍，但是推人真的无法忍受，我直接就怒了，指责他凭什么插队又推人。<br /><br />那个黄衣服一听到被指责，也立即愤怒了起来，操着经典的东北口音，开始骂骂咧咧的，甚至直接提高了嗓门给自己壮胆，仿佛电梯插队+推人是老天爷赏赐他的合法权利。<br /><br />我反驳他的理由也很直接，凭什么插队，凭什么推人，有没有素质。<br /><br />他接着愤怒，开始骂人，我十年 LOL 也不是白打的，骂得比他更有文采，内涵更丰富，更能恶心他。<br /><br /><br />一直对骂到他到了楼层下了电梯，我才罢休。<br /><br /><br />期间还有一些人的反应很有意思：<br />1 还在 1L 的时候，我和他争吵的时候，另一个黄色衣服的送外卖的，只是路过，然后只是听到了争吵，就开始指责我。他并不需要知道发生了什么，穿着黄衣服的就该帮着黄衣服的。<br />2 电梯里应该都是我同公司的同事，但是没有一个帮我说话的，不过我也不苛求这些，大家都是少一事不如多一事。身后那个因为被插队而没上电梯的人也只是无奈的看着我俩对骂。<br /><br /><br />可惜的是当时保安不在，在的话肯定能帮我伸张正义","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819766","replies":95,"created_ts":1638507579,"created":"12:59:39","title":"就在刚刚，我在办公楼的电梯里和一个送外卖的骂了起来。遇到这种情况，你们会怎么处理？","author":"wasd6267016","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wasd6267016","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ba2d/959a/200647_mini.png?m=1636693807"},{"id":819698,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1638325006","description":"很惭愧，还没有，一度怀疑自己的智商","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819698","replies":78,"created_ts":1638493848,"created":"09:10:48","title":"毕业两年半的朋友们还有没实现经济独立的吗","author":"BlackFri","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/BlackFri","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/44988fa6a9a9bc73d259bed42740c908?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":819683,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"早上好！请问大家 iOS 访问 V2EX 用什么客服端","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819683","replies":70,"created_ts":1638488447,"created":"07:40:47","title":"请问大家 iOS 访问 V2EX 用什么客服端","author":"yyingx","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yyingx","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e8009030978ee5f8c3b2886637b108d9?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":819780,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","description":"<p>调整了间距 &amp; 更改颜色。</p>\n<h2>使用方式</h2>\n<p>设置 &gt; 自定义 CSS</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">@import \"https://sunflower-assets.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/css/v2ex.css\";\n</code></pre>\n<h2>效果预览</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://sunflower-assets.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/images/v2ex/v2ex_light.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://sunflower-assets.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/images/v2ex/v2ex_light-detail.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://sunflower-assets.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/images/v2ex/v2ex_dark.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://sunflower-assets.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/images/v2ex/v2ex_dark_detail.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819780","replies":67,"created_ts":1638510645,"created":"13:50:45","title":"我搞了一个 V2EX 类某乎的主题，支持亮色与暗色🌙☀️","author":"viewweiwu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/viewweiwu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3317/c0a5/301659_mini.png?m=1638447206"},{"id":819771,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","description":"<p>为了实现代码检视（ Pull Request ）这个功能，公司从 SVN 切换到了 Git ，但是不少人遇到了下面的问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>没有理解 Git 的工作区、暂存区、仓库区、远端之间的关系，用 SVN 的思维去使用 Git ，比如会通过删除工作区文件、再拉取代码这种方式来回退代码。</li>\n<li>在修改工作区文件后，没有 commit 或者 stash ，就 pull 代码，导致提示冲突，因为不熟练所以不知道如何解决。</li>\n<li>之前 SVN 仓库中有很多需要经常修改的大二进制文件，初期迁移的时候没有用 LFS 管理，导致 Git 仓库庞大，clone 要花很长时间。</li>\n<li>使用 LFS 后，因为各个用户终端配置不一样，可能有的人没有装 LFS ，提交后，其他人再 pull ，会出现很多奇怪的问题。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>感觉从 SVN 切换到 Git ，还是要慎重，至少要培训熟练。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819771","replies":64,"created_ts":1638509355,"created":"13:29:15","title":"公司从 SVN 切换到 Git 的那些坑","author":"villivateur","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/villivateur","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_mini.png?m=1635395897"},{"id":819829,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","description":"<p>看了这个微博有点怀疑了\n<a href=\"https://weibo.com/2568228607/L4ijQr7zO\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://weibo.com/2568228607/L4ijQr7zO</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wGOFePz.png\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://i.imgur.com/wGOFePz.png</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819829","replies":59,"created_ts":1638519081,"created":"16:11:21","title":"程序员不想卷了去考公真的是好的选择吗？","author":"asd7160","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/asd7160","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8a227f7518abbefc8d457746bca01bb1?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":819826,"node":"随想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/random","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453","description":"我现在人在青岛，<br />不出意外的话也会死在青岛，<br />挺好的。<br /><br />我已经签了器官捐献，<br />等我死了，<br />器官都拿去捐一捐，<br />青岛离海那么近，<br />遗体烧成灰，<br />我女儿把我装罐子里，<br />到了海上打开盖儿往海里一扬就行了。<br />丧葬费一千多，<br />甚至连车都不用打。<br />多省劲儿。<br /><br />一点儿都不想埋在地下，<br />不自由。<br />孩子要是心情不好，<br />想我了就去海边看看我，<br />妈妈永远在大海里陪着她。<br />不想我，<br />走到海边也能顺便看看我，<br />我也看看她。<br />去哪个陵园能有去海边方便，<br />是吧。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819826","replies":58,"created_ts":1638518503,"created":"16:01:43","title":"看到“葬礼歌单”的帖子，想问有多少人像我一样，准备死后把骨灰撒海里的？","author":"faustina2018","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/faustina2018","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f13/d763/287238_mini.png?m=1629108246"},{"id":819772,"node":"硬件","node_url"